<p>You <strong><a href="https://blog.datawrapper.de/color-keys-for-data-visualizations/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">designed a useful (and fun!) color key for your data visualization</a></strong> to explain to your readers what your colors mean? Great! Now you’ll want to make sure people don’t forget<strong> those associations between colors and categories</strong>. This article explores a few ways to do so: </p>



